                            <comment id="13019502" author="brian.stansberry" created="Wed, 12 Nov 2014 12:38:18 -0500"  >&lt;p&gt;David, per chat discussion it looks like you are looking at this in terms of a remoting change. If there&apos;s anything we must do to mitigate this, let me know.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I find it a bit odd that RemotingModelControllerClient.close() is calling channelAssociation.shutdownNow &lt;b&gt;after&lt;/b&gt; closing the channel and endpoint, and if were done first perhaps the result could be that ManagementChannelReceiver stops registering itself after each message. But there&apos;s probably still a race there anyway and I don&apos;t want to start mucking with this stuff unless I need to.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
